Emergency services are at the scene of the crash in Jozini, KZN. KWAZULU-NATAL - A major accident has taken place in Jozini, KwaZulu-Natal. Several people have been reported critically injured after a truck ploughed into cars and pedestrians. READ: Six injured in Durban crash The number of casualties has not been confirmed. Paramedics and emergency services are currently trying to free people trapped in the wreckage. More details to follow.